title: Kangaroo Punch 2022  | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 57
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
THE BABES are on the road doing stand up comedy together in cities across the USA! BABEFEST 2021 IS ON AND IS INDEED LIT!! A few more stops left this week! Come party with us at our show on NEW YEARS EVE 2022!!!! The babes are in the green room of their show in Sugarland Texas. They vent about bad hotel experiences and the literal nightmare that happened to Sal in Texas. Kangaroos are SUS!!!
Rate us on iTunes!
